  <entry>
    <title>手把手教你搭建自己的博客</title>
    <url>/2024/01/08/%E6%89%8B%E6%8A%8A%E6%89%8B%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>本文主要讲述使用Hexo模板搭建自己的博客。</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h2 id="一安装node.js软件">一、安装node.js软件</h2>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nodejs.org download</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="二安装git软件">二、安装git软件</h2>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">https://git-scm.com/download/win</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="三创建博客">三、创建博客</h2>
<blockquote>
<p>参考教程：</p>
<p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Yb411a7ty/?spm_id_from=333.1007.top_right_bar_window_history.content.click&amp;vd_source=03597a48d90ef1391464cd8a60de285d">手把手教你从0开始搭建自己的个人博客
|无坑版视频教程| hexo_哔哩哔哩_bilibili</a></p>
</blockquote>
<p>### 1、建立文件夹mono0826Blog &gt; win10用户： （1）f:，进入f盘
（2）mkdir mono0826Blog，创建mono0826Blog文件夹 &gt; linux用户：
直接在主目录下创建 mkdir mono0826Blog</p>
<p>### 2、hexo init 初始化一个博客 ### 3、hexo s启动博客</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Hexo is running at http://localhost:4000/</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="hexo-n-手把手教你搭建自己的博客">4、hexo n
"手把手教你搭建自己的博客"</h3>
<pre><code>路径：/source/_posts</code></pre>
<h3 id="编辑博客">5、编辑博客</h3>
<p>可以用typora软件进行编辑 ### 6、hexo clean ### 7、hexo g生成 ###
8、将博客部署到github上 ### 9、github上创建仓库 &gt;
必须时自己的用户名.github.io</p>
<h3 id="在mono0826blog目录下安装">10、在mono0826Blog目录下安装</h3>
<blockquote>
<p>win10：</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>linux： <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm install --save hexo-deployer-git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="设置config.yml文件">11、 设置config.yml文件</h3>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">		type: git</span><br><span class="line">		repo: https://github.com/mono0826/mono0826.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">		branch: master</span><br><span class="line"> 保存退出</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="hexo-d上传">12、hexo d上传</h3>
<p>如果出现 &gt; error 403</p>
<blockquote>
<p>解决办法：生成ssh钥匙
将config.yml文件中的ropo改为git@github.com:mono0826/mono0826.github.io.git
再hexo d即可</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="在github仓库中就能看到上传的文件">13、在github仓库中就能看到上传的文件</h3>
<h3 id="通过mono0826.github.io访问">14、通过mono0826.github.io访问</h3>
<blockquote>
<p>如果出现404，打开settings界面，找到pages，找到Branch，改为master，save即可</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="四博客页面优化">四、博客页面优化</h2>
<h3 id="下载主题">1、下载主题</h3>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia.git themes/yilia</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="配置到自己的博客">2、配置到自己的博客</h3>
<p>修改config.yml 找到themes，改为yilia</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean </span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="显示本文结束">3、显示<strong>本文结束</strong></h3>
<p>（1）在_macro目录下，新建文件</p>
<blockquote>
<p>passage-end-tag.njk</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>文件内容为：</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    {% if not is_index %}</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div style="text-align:center;color: #ccc;font-size:14px;"&gt;------ 本文结束------&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    {% endif %}</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>（2）打开post.njk文件</p>
<p>在</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">{#####################}</span><br><span class="line">{### END POST BODY ###}</span><br><span class="line">{#####################}</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>后面添加</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">{#####################}</span><br><span class="line">{### 本文结束 ###}</span><br><span class="line">{#####################}</span><br><span class="line">&lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    {% if not is_index %}</span><br><span class="line">    {% include 'passage-end-tag.njk' %}</span><br><span class="line">    {% endif %}</span><br><span class="line"> &lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>保存。</p>
<p>（3）打开themes目录下的config.yml</p>
<p>在末尾添加</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 文章末尾添加“本文结束”标记</span><br><span class="line">passage_end_tag:</span><br><span class="line">  enabled: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">在终端输入</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>即可看到</p>
<figure>
<img src="/.io//image-20240108190121244.png" alt="文章末尾显示本文结束">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">文章末尾显示本文结束</figcaption>
</figure>
<h3 id="显示文字总数和阅读时间">4、显示文字总数和阅读时间</h3>
<p>（1）在终端输入</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm install hexo-symbols-count-time</span><br><span class="line">cnpm install hexo-word-counter</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>（2）在blog目录下的config.yml末尾输入</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 显示阅读时间</span><br><span class="line">symbols_count_time:</span><br><span class="line"># 每篇文章显示</span><br><span class="line">  symbols: true</span><br><span class="line">  time: true</span><br><span class="line"># 文章底部显示</span><br><span class="line">  total_symbols: false</span><br><span class="line">  total_time: false</span><br><span class="line"># 是否统计代码块</span><br><span class="line">  exclude_codeblock: false</span><br><span class="line">  awl: 2    </span><br><span class="line">  wpm: 275</span><br><span class="line">  suffix: "mins."</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>结果为：</p>
<img src="/.io//01/08/%E6%89%8B%E6%8A%8A%E6%89%8B%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image-20240108190512463.png" class title="image-20240108190512463">
<h3 id="显示搜索功能">5、显示搜索功能</h3>
<p>终端输入</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm install hexo-generator-searchdb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在themes目录下打开config.yml文件</p>
<p>找到local_search，设置为true</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Local Search</span><br><span class="line"># Dependencies: https://github.com/next-theme/hexo-generator-searchdb</span><br><span class="line">local_search:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  # If auto, trigger search by changing input.</span><br><span class="line">  # If manual, trigger search by pressing enter key or search button.</span><br><span class="line">  trigger: auto</span><br><span class="line">  # Show top n results per article, show all results by setting to -1</span><br><span class="line">  top_n_per_article: 1</span><br><span class="line">  # Unescape html strings to the readable one.</span><br><span class="line">  unescape: false</span><br><span class="line">  # Preload the search data when the page loads.</span><br><span class="line">  preload: false</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="显示文章摘要">6、显示文章摘要</h3>
<p>在写博客的时候使用</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!-- more --&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>隔开，前面的内容为摘要，后面的为主要内容</p>
<h3 id="修改博客字体">7、修改博客字体</h3>
<blockquote>
<p>参考链接：<a href="https://spartazhc.github.io/2020/06/03/Next主题字体配置/">Next主题字体配置
| spartazhc's blog</a></p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="代码可复制">8、代码可复制</h3>
<blockquote>
<p>参考链接：<a href="https://www.gaoyuanqi.cn/hexo-next-copy1/">Hexo代码块添加一键复制功能
| 雨园博客 (gaoyuanqi.cn)</a></p>
</blockquote>
